  "history": {
    "title": "Our Story",
    "p1": "Los Grisales was born from a deep love for the Colombian coffee region. In the mountains of Risaralda, among the lush green coffee plantations and the unmistakable aroma of freshly roasted coffee, a family dream was forged.",
